Dev Docs for this section
Adding a favourite There are two ways to add a favourite.
Star icon Click the star icon A dialog will open, confirm the details and click &ldquo;Done&rdquo;
Add favourite button Another way to add a favourite is through the Add Favourite button in a blank tab A dialog will open, confirm the details and click &ldquo;Done&rdquo;
Displaying favourites Favourites will be displayed in the favourites bar as well as in a blank tab as quick shortcuts Editing a favourite Right click on a bookmark and click &ldquo;Edit&rdquo; then change the details and click &ldquo;done&rdquo;
